data.description:
PRICE REDUCED, AND $7000 IN SELLER CONCESSIONS! Back on the Market at No Fault of the Seller!!!   Inspections have already been done on this home, with minimal issues being cited.  Please contact listing agent for a copy of the inspection.  

Wanting a HOME, To Make your Own, This is the Place for you!  Use the $7000 in Sellers Concessions for Cosmetic Updates, Closing Costs or Whatever you choose.  This Strong Home has amazing bones but needs updating.  Visit this 3 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath Home.  This adorable place is full of amazing memories, but is ready to Welcome Another Family HOME!  Don't miss this sweet kitchen, with built in Booth Seating, a Huge Family Room with a Fireplace, and a Large Basement, that could be a Man Cave, with a 4th Non Conforming Bedroom.  Also, you will find additional Built in Storge in the Family Room and Basement.  

Wake up or Relax in the Evening to this Amazing Sun Room, that can be used all year long.  The Garage will Park 2 vehicles/trucks easily, and has a Huge Loft, that could be used for storage or a work shop.  
 
This home is being sold "AS IS".
